{"tid":2342781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭月娥提醒警員小心防疫","createTime":"2020-12-27T11:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T23:29:08.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd61e05196464d27b757b011773d4527ef9bd7c","tid":2342781,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥到深圳灣管制站，了解「回港易」實施情況。<br />\n<br />\n「辛苦了。」<br />\n<br />\n「你可否讓我看看&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「好。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是我爸爸的，這是我的。」<br />\n<br />\n「你過來時已經轉色？」<br />\n<br />\n「是的。」<br />\n<br />\n「有無一些特別個案？」<br />\n<br />\n「沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n她指，「回港易」實施約一個月，有近兩萬名香港居民由廣東省或澳門回港豁免強制檢疫。她之後經屯赤娥提醒警員小心防疫連接路到港珠澳大橋管制站視察，了解入境流程，提醒警員要小心防疫，又跟海關的搜查犬合照。"},{"pid":"fa975899bcafac6589a9f77616db9ed01433e5ae","tid":2342781,"uid":96704,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"以為係甜故"},{"pid":"bac7096635fca7993da6e5ffa98f2ac5fec064c3","tid":2342781,"uid":23445,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"必須好好獎勵你"},{"pid":"4465b254ebf16ee3bac48caded1f4f875ddcad07","tid":2342781,"uid":238340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"黎，獎你哋班狗狗同月娥做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c55bfa017fc63aed8cbad7c8fd1fa50fee3f7e3","tid":2342781,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"警員做嘢關你林鄭撚事!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4cd684f0b3b476ae6814c09473fa00ab45e4e0","tid":2342781,"uid":14422,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kW0hBJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkW0hBJM.png&h=026af16a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b1a5d8e72a08a9c283f0ebae6db73af4f6e5e7d","tid":2342781,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"